                  查詢嶺東科技大學館藏





系統識別號
U0103-3107201412034900


論文名稱(中文)
 服務業從業人員婚姻態度－以女性美髮從業人員為例


論文名稱(英文)
Marital Attitude of Service Industry Practitioners - Cases Study of Female A Hairdressers Practitioners



校院名稱
嶺東科技大學


系所名稱(中)
流行設計研究所


系所名稱(英)
Graduate Institute of fashion design 


學年度
102


學期
2


出版年
103


研究生(中文)
許毓菁


研究生(英文)
Yu-Ching Hsu


學號
A1MH003


學位類別
碩士


語文別
中文


口試日期
2013-07-02


論文頁數
84頁


口試委員
指導教授-張翠園委員-謝俊宏委員-陳高生


中文關鍵字

婚姻態度        
                      
                  女性        
                      
                  美髮業        
                      
                  擇偶條件        
                
              


英文關鍵字

female hairdressers        
                        
                    service industry        
                        
                    woman        
                        
                    marriage preferences        
                  
                


學科別分類



中文摘要

                  本研究主要以女性美髮從業人員為研究對象，因美髮從業人員的工作環境上，工時較長，在經濟上更為獨立，且常見未婚美髮從業人員有晚婚與不婚情況發生。故本研究探討其對婚姻的態度及想法，藉由調查法探討未婚女性美髮從業人員之工作環境條件對內在自身條件、擇偶條件、婚姻態度，內在自身條件對擇偶條件、婚姻態度，及擇偶條件對婚姻態度間的關係及相互的影響性。研究結果發現：1. 女性美髮從業人員在工作環境條件、內在自身條件、擇偶條件與婚姻態度的認知上介於普通到同意之間，在認同程度上接近同意。2. 部份未婚女性美髮從業人員之背景變項(年齡、教育程度、家庭結構、宗教信仰)對其工作環境條件、內在自身條件、婚姻態度在認知上有顯著差異。3. 女性美髮從業人員的工作環境條件對內在自身條件、擇偶條件與婚姻態度，內在自身條件對擇偶條件與婚姻態度，及擇偶條件對婚姻態度等構面皆有顯著正向影響。



英文摘要

                  The present study is an attempt to understand the trends toward late marriage and non-marriage of female hairdressers. Singlehood levels in this service group are high because they work long hours and become more financially independent. This study examines unmarried female hairdresser’s attitude and behavior toward marriage. Findings from sample survey are used to investigate the relationship and influence among working environment, internal-self-condition, marriage preference, marriage attitude of female hairdressers practitioners’ characteristics in practitioners of service industry. Shown below are the research results: (1)Female hairdressers’s perception toward working environment, internal-self-condition, marriage preference, marriage attitude is between neutral to consent, and their recognization toward these factors is close to acceptance.(2)Portion of unmarried female hairdressers has significant difference in recognizing working environment, internal-self-condition, marriage preferences, and marriage attitude due to their backgroud variable (age, education, family structure, and religion).  (3)There would be positive influences of working environment on internal-self-condition, marriage preferences and marriage attitude.  So is the internal-self-condition on marriage preferences and marriage attitude. So is marriage preferences on marriage attitude.



